room_title: Escape room "Unsolved Case" by Epic Escape Game in Cheyenne
room_description:
You’ve been a detective for over 30 years and its finally time to retire, the only problem is, there’s still one open case haunting you...

This case involves a man that was never found and it remains the only unsolved skyjacking in U.S. history. Now, for the first time, after nearly a decade of silence a tip came through. Can You Solve the Mystery in the last hour of your career?
